features: [Durable Material] The car interior cleaner is made of ABS plastic material, which is sturdy and durable, not easy to break or deform, and is equipped with a washable and reusable covering cloth. The covering cloth is made of high-quality ultrafine fiber material, which is high-quality and durable, and can be used for a long time.

[Detachable Ultrafine Fiber Cloth Pad]The car window cleaning tool includes three ultra-fine fiber pads, which are easy to replace and can be used both dry and wet. The surface of the fiber cloth is finely treated to easily attract, fix, and remove dirt and dust from the surface of the car windshield. It can clean your vehicle well and there will be no streaks after cleaning.
[Retractable Handle] Durable and ergonomic handle, easy to use and effortless. Scalable features help to reach difficult to reach areas without further injury to the back.

[180 ° Rotating Head]Adopting a rotating square head design, it can fully contact the glass and rotate 180 degrees, making it very suitable for the glass surface and easy to clean the bottom of the car window or some difficult to reach areas.

[Widely Used] Windshield cleaning tools are easy to use, just put a piece of microfiber cloth over your head, spray with water, and then start cleaning. Suitable for all sizes of cars, SUVs, trucks, jeeps, UTVs, ATVs, etc.
